00:02:08.979 --> 00:02:13.740
And I think that it's really
hard to write something new or

00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:16.780
to create something new when
you don't know what's come

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:18.290
before you.

00:02:18.290 --> 00:02:22.300
So I'd like to talk about the
process that I used to develop

00:02:22.300 --> 00:02:26.760
"The PDT Cocktail Book" and I'd
like to introduce a big

00:02:26.760 --> 00:02:29.680
