00:02:37.050 --> 00:02:37.950
about half an hour.

00:02:37.950 --> 00:02:41.770
But as I said before, I believe
that the internet,

00:02:41.770 --> 00:02:47.430
Google, YouTube, Wikipedia, on
and on, and on his change the

00:02:47.430 --> 00:02:51.450
