00:42:08.950 --> 00:42:10.730
one of the things I realized
working with the New York

00:42:10.730 --> 00:42:13.940
media is that really all they
write about, God bless them

00:42:13.940 --> 00:42:15.200
is-- what's new and
what's hot.

00:42:15.200 --> 00:42:18.940
So if you want to remain in the
media and become popular,

00:42:18.940 --> 00:42:20.240
you have to constantly evolve.

00:42:20.240 --> 00:42:24.170
So it's hard to say in the
bigger picture how long some

00:42:24.170 --> 00:42:25.850
