that logic to some of the

00:43:06.820 --> 00:43:08.330
trends that are going on.

00:43:08.330 --> 00:43:10.950
If it's delicious, if it allows
you to see and be seen,

00:43:10.950 --> 00:43:13.400
if it's efficient, I think
it'll stay around.

